Run the following commands on the terminal

docker pull wordpress:4.3.1
docker pull mysql:5.7

In the folder where stack.yml is stored, run the following command
Run docker stack deploy -c stack.yml wordpress 
(or docker-compose -f stack.yml up),


wait for it to initialize completely, 

and visit http://swarm-ip:8080, http://localhost:8080, or http://host-ip:8080 (as appropriate).
